---
alwaysApply: true
---

Source of truth:
- Follow docs/spec-cursor.txt and docs/plan.md.
- Implement ONLY the current commit step from plan.md. Do not do future work.

Working style:
- Keep changes minimal and reviewable.
- If requirements conflict or are unclear, STOP and ask. Do not guess.
- Enforce server-side authorization; never rely on UI-only restrictions.

Quality gates before “done”:
- Backend: dotnet build must pass.
- Frontend: npm run lint must pass.
- Provide: (1) changed files summary, (2) commands to run/verify, (3) any assumptions.

Code quality:
- No dead code, no commented-out code, no “TODO” without a clear next step.
- Prefer simple solutions over clever abstractions.
- Names in code/docs: English.
